cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.BIO. 

The paper deals with the problem of automatic lesion classification from OCT images in the upper aerodigestive tract. This involves the use of deep learning approaches for decision support. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of transfer learning methods, which are commonly used in deep learning, hence cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories. As the paper deals with medical imaging and diagnosis, cs.MED (Medical Imaging) and cs.BIO (Bioinformatics) are also possible categories.
